Mike Lookinland https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mike_Lookinland 0 Not to be confused with American soccer player Mike Lookingland.Michael Paul Lookinland (born December 19, 1960) is an American former actor. He is best known for his role as the youngest brother, Bobby Brady, on The Brady Bunch from 1969 until 1974.
